These are script to use Compute Canada on-demand instances.

see https://rqchp.ca/?mod=cms&pageId=1380&lang=EN&

Regular cluster instances

32 GiB memory
2 x AMD Opteron(tm) Processor 6172 (24 cores)
504 GiB of instance storage
64-bit platform
I/O performance: Infiniband 7:2
Lustre storage
API name: qwork@mp2


Fast cluster instance

32 GiB memory
2 x AMD Opteron(tm) Processor 6172 (24 cores)
instance storage
64-bit platform
I/O performance: Infiniband 1:1
Lustre storage
API name: qfbb@mp2


High memory cluster instance

256 GiB memory
AMD Opteron (48 cores)
instance storage
64-bit platform
I/O performance: Infiniband 1:1
Lustre storage
API name: qfat256@mp2


High memory cluster large instance

qfat512@mp2

512 GiB memory
AMD Opteron (48 cores)
instance storage
64-bit platform
I/O performance: Infiniband 1:1
Lustre storage
API name: qfat512@mp2

